      "content": "wait, you said it might be appendicitis but then you told me to just take the meds and sleep? i'm confused. are you sure it's not just cramps? i really don't want to go to the er if i can avoid it, it's so expensive and i'm just tired. if i take the ibuprofen and codeine like you said, will that definitely help it settle down by morning?",
